Agent File Handoff

Active intake buckets:
- agent-file-handoff/Content
- agent-file-handoff/Improvement

Processing rule:
Before broad work, inspect active intake. Use files as source material, record what was used in .uai/intake-outcome-ledger.uai, then move or summarize processed material only after review.

Outcome values:
- accepted
- partially_accepted
- deferred
- rejected

Completion gate:
No final report may claim handoff complete unless active intake was inspected and the outcome ledger records the result.
